headline: Leidos hires Daryle Lademan to lead corporate strategy activities
summary: Leidos (NYSE: LDOS) is bringing on Daryle Lademan as its new senior vice president of corporate strategy, a role in which she'll lead company-level growth strategies, strategic partnerships and investments, strategy execution and special projects.

headline: Leidos completes successful test launch of a Small Cruise Missile
summary: Leidos in November successfully completed a guided flight test of their Small Cruise Missile (SCM), known as Black Arrow, from an AC-130J aircraft. The test demonstrated aircraft compatibility, system performance, waypoint uplinks, guidance accuracy as well as integration with the Naval Surface Warfare Center Battle Management System (BMS).
